➜广东诗人小隐：相见欢．东湖菊花展（外六首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/437645118_100115135	30229
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201211/8a31d98272e7425f9dbfbcb700e0d7f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>相见欢．东湖菊花展</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋天醉了天穹，菊香浓。多少风云淡去，晚来冬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妆为俏，花来笑，自由衷。人羡东篱知己，乐相同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201211/d79f083be9274fdcac26c06211a85b6a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题（题图）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">枝枝冬雪侵，寒岁尽春林。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瑟瑟山头鸟，无声对客吟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201211/9dcdf371c1f54bc29ab3fb259582a853.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
