➜河南诗人卧龙：暗香随风
http://www.sohu.com/a/437645698_100115135	30555
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201211/8fe91ec286964be8b014767a39437488.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>暗香随风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/卧龙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晨步觉寒冷，沿堤负手行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寻梅深屐齿，浅浅暗香生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201211/84741af9c0574485afe40da444c4f625.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>高云伟，笔名：卧龙，1962年出生，河南南阳油田工作。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201211/fd350d69bd0e4875ac01e938e22528e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
