➜广西诗人陈熠明：七绝•逍遥玉树唱风流（外二首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/437647444_100115135	31012
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201211/efee1c67693d486aad73e3a190fccc7d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•逍遥玉树唱风流</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹心热恋爱春秋，对影双成话里头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月难得真有梦，逍遥玉树唱风流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201211/a6b751a1e1f0454fba1a158485fdd70e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝•绚丽云霞共海天（题图）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗作者•陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥遥此去话尘缘，绚丽云霞共海天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泪洒清风流水去，别离此刻更缠绵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201211/ccbdcfb413e04cbb81da85b8456c2e41.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
