➜广东诗人辉哥：入秋（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/437648553_100115135	31374
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201211/1e91aca462e2475aacee8433ebeb0925.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>入秋（11月27日深圳正式气象学入秋）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天冷风干日晴柔，菊黄水碧意清幽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">懒秋迟到冬君近，可盼围炉酒一瓯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201211/f18a5c7d09204c0291e24d77eae2735d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冬晨 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋后低温连日现，苍天急急召冬君；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风中喜见骄阳媚，街上难逢短袖人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201211/f580dcf0e68243d2acdbe321a12da4a6.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
