➜河南诗人王琦伟：七绝·大雪（外二首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/437654192_100115135	33127
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201211/942524a9683f4d90b4cc9e7bc51625f7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·大雪（平水韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北国琼花暗溢香，临风傲骨着银装。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一行玉印谁雕出，踏雪寻梅雅兴藏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.07</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201211/8a3422b2742d43e4bd8725d87b951310.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·愁（平水韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回望天空月似钩，辉光难掩几多愁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独行步道灯相伴，谁可倾谈笑语留。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.07</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
