➜宁夏诗人梁继权（凉亭）：七绝·肥了春潮漫断桥（外七首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/437657142_100115135	34346
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201211/c83ce8f0b7124f9fa6c15dcc675fcf5e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·肥了春潮漫断桥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者／梁继权（凉亭）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">款步三娥百媚撩，兜风一路两峰摇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惹来谛视心怦动，肥了春潮漫断桥。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>注：①诗以新韵）。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>②视频截图于网络。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201211/5e18c53001c3447aa5af02dbd956202f.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">（诗人星连摄于徐州）</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·淘气鬼（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者／梁继权（凉亭）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已过蹒跚耍赖皮，紧盯老母不相离。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
