➜听尘居士：杂诗八首
http://www.sohu.com/a/437661176_100115135	36780
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201211/b3f732cdc97441b9bfdcf36291b330c8.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">（诗人星连摄于徐州）</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一、（题图）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思近岁晚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落雪掩绿痕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北风寒入骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冻煞有心人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二、江湖客</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江湖流浪客</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流浪在江湖</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">偶遇一知己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满天霜雪无</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>三、秋愁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">耐得清秋晚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独向一扁舟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰玉惊鸿客</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芊芊染故愁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>四、随吟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒梅艳艳冰雪残</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
